      "content": "i know you're just an ai, i'm not expecting you to fix me. it's just... talking to people feels like so much work. they just give me those generic lines and try to make me feel \"better\" when nothing is actually better. it just feels like i'm carrying this huge, heavy stone around every single day and i'm just so tired of holding it. i just want the weight to stop. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to rest without everything feeling so heavy.",
